=Description=

"Grounded in relationships, our mission is to embark on a collaborative vulnerable exploratory process of reorientation and remembrance. You could think of it as '''an ongoing human~nature~culture restoration project'''. This involves practices rooted in a devotion to being present. Through this process, you, as a human being, can gain a clearer understanding of your place as part of this shared journey, not only as a human being, but also as a Relational Being. Our goal is to encourage mindful and caring engagement, in collaboration with the shared ecology you are intimately intertwined with, where inclusive creative processes are rooted in multispecies collaborations between us humans, and our more-than-human companions.   By navigating reality from this eco-cosmic position and context you are better able to embrace the magnificent relationships you have all around you that exist beyond the human-centered realm. Through slowing down, opening up, and allowing for this field of connectivity and relationality into your life, ideally you will be better able to see that you belong as part of this living planet, along with the rest of nature."


